RAD_LOVS.LOV_QUERY: SELECT CONTRACT_REF_NO, LATEST_EVENT_SEQ_NO FROM OLTB_CONTRACT WHERE PRODUCT_TYPE IN ('L', 'D') AND EXISTS (SELECT 1 FROM SMVWS_USER_BRANCHES B WHERE B.BRANCH_CODE = OLTB_CONTRACT.BRANCH)
SELECT BRANCH_CODE, BRANCH_NAME FROM OLTMS_BRANCH WHERE RECORD_STAT = 'O' AND AUTH_STAT = 'A'

SELECT AC_GL_NO, AC_GL_CCY, AC_GL_DESC FROM OLTBS_ACCOUNT A WHERE ((BRANCH_CODE = ?) OR (BRANCH_CODE IS NOT NULL OR AC_OR_GL = 'G') AND GL_ACLASS_TYPE <> '5' AND AC_GL_REC_STATUS = 'O' AND NVL(BRANCH_CODE, '$$') IN (GLOBAL.CURRENT_BRANCH, '$$')) AND EXISTS (SELECT * FROM OLVWS_PROD_ACNT_ACCESS X WHERE X.AC_GL_NO = A.AC_GL_NO AND X.PRODUCT_CODE = ?) ORDER BY AC_GL_NO
